Dialogue: 11,0:22:12.89,0:22:17.89,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Vibration, an undelivered emotion
Dialogue: 11,0:22:24.78,0:22:30.62,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}This place exists as a sequence of layers
Dialogue: 11,0:22:30.82,0:22:36.75,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Of worlds recursing within worlds
Dialogue: 11,0:22:38.42,0:22:41.54,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Although time is irreversible
Dialogue: 11,0:22:41.54,0:22:44.25,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}These sectors remain unaccessed
Dialogue: 11,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.30,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Why did I receive this vision of a kiss
Dialogue: 11,0:22:46.30,0:22:49.26,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Like a flash-forward?
Dialogue: 11,0:22:50.39,0:22:55.31,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}It came from so close—an outrageously large distance
Dialogue: 11,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.64,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I can only conclude that our existence is defined by “0”s and “1”s
Dialogue: 11,0:22:59.64,0:23:02.98,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}In which I can be found right here
Dialogue: 11,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.28,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I'll tell you my feelings that I keep inside
Dialogue: 11,0:23:07.28,0:23:10.41,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}I remain in solitude, while in hold of
Dialogue: 11,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.16,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}A countless number of infinitely expansive universes
Dialogue: 11,0:23:16.16,0:23:19.58,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}That's why I'll make sure
Dialogue: 11,0:23:19.58,0:23:22.67,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}For the sake of your tomorrow
Dialogue: 11,0:23:22.67,0:23:28.47,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}That the blasphemy of the God ruling this universe
Dialogue: 11,0:23:28.84,0:23:31.93,Worldline Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-4.5}Will never be repeated
